<P>> Excellent ideas, you have really put a lot of thought into this

<BR>&gt; have you had PvP experience in other onkine games such as UO?
<P>Yea, I played UO baja shard as a pk for about 8 months, as well as many years of pk mud experience. About UO, do't associate me with those wimp PKs who cheat (dupe gold etc..) and hunt down the naked miners with 10 people in their group. I hunt solo most of the time, it is a lot harder to find good even battles but when one does occur it a fun 10 minute dual at least. Anyway I feel that action in UO is pretty slow, not fast enough for the minds to boil if you know what I mean.
<BR>
